'''母嬰之家醜聞'''指1922年至1998年間，出生並收養於[[愛爾蘭共和國|愛爾蘭]]{{le|母嬰之家|Bon Secours Mother and Baby Home}}（Mother and Baby Homes）的57,000名嬰兒有9,000名死亡（15%），比[[愛爾蘭共和國|愛爾蘭]]同期的[[嬰兒死亡率|嬰兒死亡率]]高出一倍。母嬰之家是[[愛爾蘭天主教|愛爾蘭天主教]]修女營運，專門[[收養|收養]][[未婚產子|未婚產子]]，而由於[[未婚產子|未婚產子]]在天主教視為「[[罪_(宗教)|罪孽]]」（sin）和禁忌，孕婦被強逼入住，期間屢遭宗教侮辱，之後再被強逼與兒女分離。<ref>{{cite news|first=Kara|last=Fox|title=Ireland's 'brutally misogynistic culture' saw the death of 9,000 children in mother and baby homes, report finds|date=2021-01-12|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2021/01/12/europe/ireland-mother-baby-homes-final-report-intl/index.html|access-date=2021-01-13|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112233902/https://edition.cnn.com/2021/01/12/europe/ireland-mother-baby-homes-final-report-intl/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

事件最先因為2014年史學家在[[戈尔韦郡|戈尔韦郡]]{{le|蒂厄姆|Tuam}}發現了一個有796名嬰兒屍骨的[[亂葬崗|亂葬崗]]，經比對建築[[圖則|圖則]]，部份屍骨的位置在當年[[化糞池|化糞池]]的位置，引起輿論大嘩（註：[[化糞池|化糞池]]後來在1930年代廢棄）。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thejournal.ie/catherine-corless-tuam-mother-and-baby-home-3268501-Mar2017/|title=She was right: How Catherine Corless uncovered what happened in Tuam|last=Bohan|first=Christine|publisher=TheJournal.ie|date=2017-03-03|accessdate=2017-03-21|archive-date=2017-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322112040/http://www.thejournal.ie/catherine-corless-tuam-mother-and-baby-home-3268501-Mar2017/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/republic-of-ireland/mass-grave-of-796-babies-found-in-septic-tank-at-catholic-orphanage-in-tuam-galway-30327483.html|title=Mass grave of 796 babies found in septic tank at Catholic orphanage in Tuam, Galway|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|date=2014-06-04|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924114448/http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/republic-of-ireland/mass-grave-of-796-babies-found-in-septic-tank-at-catholic-orphanage-in-tuam-galway-30327483.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Almost 800 infants buried in unmarked graves in Tuam, County Galway|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-27681076|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=2014-06-03|accessdate=2014-07-19|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131214711/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-27681076|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/03/13/a-survivor-recalls-the-mother-and-baby-home-at-tuam-in-ireland-where-friends-just-disappeared-one-after-the-other/|title=The 'mother and baby home' at Tuam, Ireland, where friends just 'disappeared, one after the other'|last=Barbash|first=Fred|date=2017-03-13|accessdate=2017-04-03|archive-date=2017-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321102646/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/03/13/a-survivor-recalls-the-mother-and-baby-home-at-tuam-in-ireland-where-friends-just-disappeared-one-after-the-other/|dead-url=no}}</ref>由[[愛爾蘭總理|愛爾蘭總理]]任命的[[皇家委員會|法定獨立調查委員會]]徹查，2021年1月12日的最終報告查出共9,000嬰兒死亡，並斷定死因多是[[呼吸道感染|呼吸道感染]]和[[腸胃炎|腸胃炎]]，報告亦查出母嬰之家疏忽、粗暴和宗教偏狹觀念的證據，但指公眾過份關注[[營養不良|營養不良]]和肢體虐待的可能性。1月13日[[愛爾蘭總理|愛爾蘭總理]]承認國家負有責任而道歉。由於愛爾蘭法律令寄養孩子難以追尋寄養的文件記錄，倖存者和倖存者之間難以聯絡，無法集中力量追尋事件真相。<ref>{{cite news |title=Mother and Baby Homes report: 9,000 children died amid high infant mortality rate |url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/social-affairs/mother-and-baby-homes-report-9-000-children-died-amid-high-infant-mortality-rate-1.4456382 |work=愛爾蘭時報 |date=2021-01-12 |accessdate=2021-01-14 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118013724/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/social-affairs/mother-and-baby-homes-report-9-000-children-died-amid-high-infant-mortality-rate-1.4456382 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=愛爾蘭上世紀「母嬰之家」9000名嬰兒死亡 政府道歉 |url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1974927/即時-國際-愛爾蘭上世紀-母嬰之家-9000名嬰兒死亡-政府道歉 |work=頭條日報 |date=2021-01-13 |accessdate=2022-01-04 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127200441/https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1974927/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%84%9B%E7%88%BE%E8%98%AD%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%96%E7%B4%80-%E6%AF%8D%E5%AC%B0%E4%B9%8B%E5%AE%B6-9000%E5%90%8D%E5%AC%B0%E5%85%92%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 背景 ==
[[業餘|業餘]][[歷史|歷史]]學家凱瑟琳Corless進行了研究，在出生的嬰兒邦·希克斯·戴母嬰之家在她的家鄉蒂厄姆，戈爾韋。她收集了數年的數據，並於2010年、2013年和2014年在當地報紙上發表了幾篇文章。她的研究表明，796名嬰兒和兒童的屍體可能被埋葬在Tuam嬰兒之家的一個未記錄的萬人塚中。<ref name=homebabies>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p06br92b |title=The Home Babies: The Amateur Historian |access-date=2018-07-28 |last=Milligan |first=Becky |date=2018-06-21 |publisher=BBC Radio 4 |archive-date=2018-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180923053001/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p06br92b |dead-url=no }}</ref>

